   8:Drivers/STM32F7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f7xx_hal_gpio.c ****   *           + Initialization and de-initialization functions
   9:Drivers/STM32F7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f7xx_hal_gpio.c ****   *           + IO operation functions
